{"tid":624713,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[點睇]易綱：5月1日起滬深港通額度擴大四倍 滬倫通爭取年內開通","createTime":"2018-04-11T01:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T02:01:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"55ad40d7abf357a149742522371d3e149ce3ca85","tid":624713,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:30:28.000Z","msg":"4月11日週三，中國央行行長易綱在博鰲亞洲論壇分論壇上稱，內地和香港從5月1日起互聯互通額度擴大，將把股市互聯互通每日額度擴大四倍。<br />\n<br />\n易綱還稱，中英兩國滬倫通進展順利，爭取2018年內開通。<br />\n<br />\n易綱同時提到，中國實施審慎的貨幣政策，&ldquo;我們沒有任何量化寬鬆、零利率政策，現在主要央行都在收緊利率，開始推出擴張，也會進行縮表，我們已經有很長時間期待這樣的政策發生，我們也已經準備好了&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n對於中國未來的金融開放，易綱指出下一步金融業開放將和匯率機制改革進行相互配合，金融監管能力將與開放程度相匹配；未來幾個月將落實六項金融業開放措施，將允許外國銀行在境內同時設立分行和子行；預計到今年6月30日金融開放措施大部分到位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3276756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwallstreetcn.com%2Farticles%2F3276756&d=kecV97b1VPlVpFLaMWGaYp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=48a5356f\" target=\"_blank\">https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3276756</a>"},{"pid":"88722c676dd0ce3e0998dbab413670ff601fb7f0","tid":624713,"uid":110740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"牛三來了"},{"pid":"5f9b0b7d16360c498fe8b0ffc103c374174ba6fa","tid":624713,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班撚屌"},{"pid":"34b8cfdbf14e23305df2186a41160316b07a0a6c","tid":624713,"uid":134128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"50000萬點終於要來了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06c2fb8ef0b4cc4bec2f935cb8ea179632651fb","tid":624713,"uid":109570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇用，依加一日用得7%，加大個額唔代表多jor人trade"},{"pid":"fa04076c268565763bfdb6590bdd1c48f13a7e2f","tid":624713,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:43:40.000Z","msg":"有人用？"},{"pid":"899b1470e5e8e6bd5acff1956aaac62413a47c84","tid":624713,"uid":52587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:46:10.000Z","msg":"加大額度係要應付黎緊6月同9月A股入摩<br />\n係屬於利好消息黎 不過要長期先見到"},{"pid":"ff369a6fc1307b7b2557dbc3de6f223a0b4cc932","tid":624713,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a06c2fb8ef0b4cc4bec2f935cb8ea179632651fb","tid":624713,"uid":109570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇用，依加一日用得7%，加大個額唔代表多jor人trade"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:46:43.000Z","msg":"家陣其實都用唔哂好似"},{"pid":"53b4a3eca7a98743ba3dbee56433ade4661b9dfe","tid":624713,"uid":109570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff369a6fc1307b7b2557dbc3de6f223a0b4cc932","tid":624713,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a06c2fb8ef0b4cc4bec2f935cb8ea179632651fb","tid":624713,"uid":109570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇用，依加一日用得7%，加大個額唔代表多jor人trade"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:46:43.000Z","msg":"家陣其實都用唔哂好似"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"除非小米個D真係黎曬香港IPO，個D就真係重大利好因素啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fc49a32819610a3eecd121d244d8515ef1ffc7","tid":624713,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:54:48.000Z","msg":"證監會：內地與香港證監會同意擴大互聯互通每日額度<br />\n0評論 2018-04-11 09:49:49 來源：金融界網站 萬興科技倒下後的反思<br />\n<br />\n證監會新聞發言人高莉表示，為完善內地與香港兩地股票市場互聯互通機制，穩步擴大資本市場雙向開放，兩地證監會同意擴大互聯互通每日額度，將滬股通及深股通每日額度分別調整為520億元人民幣，滬港通下的港股通及深港通下的港股通每日額度分別調整為420億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n這一擴大開放舉措，有助於境外長期機構投資者參與A股市場，維護市場安全平穩運行。下一步，兩地監管部門將繼續加強跨境資金流動監測和監管協作，加快落實看穿式交易監管安排，切實保障互聯互通機制平穩運行，促進兩地市場共同繁榮發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.jrj.com.cn/2018/04/11094924373121.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.jrj.com.cn%2F2018%2F04%2F11094924373121.shtml&d=kecV97b1VPlVpFLaMWGaYp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=42336cc0\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.jrj.com.cn/2018/04/11094924373121.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"842399397f99f457ed0a76766ab6eaa9c9f85a65","tid":624713,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b4a3eca7a98743ba3dbee56433ade4661b9dfe","tid":624713,"uid":109570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff369a6fc1307b7b2557dbc3de6f223a0b4cc932","tid":624713,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a06c2fb8ef0b4cc4bec2f935cb8ea179632651fb","tid":624713,"uid":109570,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇用，依加一日用得7%，加大個額唔代表多jor人trade"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:46:43.000Z","msg":"家陣其實都用唔哂好似"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"除非小米個D真係黎曬香港IPO，個D就真係重大利好因素啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T02:01:30.000Z","msg":"又話行同股不同權"}]}